MVVM hota hai model view viewmodel layer
clean arch me ek aur layer hota hai use cases
jb apna project ka size bdhta chla jata hai  viewmodel ka size bdhta chla jata hai us load ko kam krne k lite
usecases use krte hai


let say user profile  ka feature dena hai
esme do screen hoga editprofile aur viewprofile
ab jo action perform kr skte hai in do screen k liye wo apna use cases hoga
jaisa ki
getUserProfileDate(),updateUserProfilePic(),

use cases k fyda hai ki reusable hai  esko alg alg viewmodel me use kr skte hai
lets say getUserProfileDate() ki jrurt hai alg alg viewmodel me to use kr skte hai


Presentation layer -> use hota hai ui k liye
view,xml,viewmodel,composable,

Domain layer  -> it contains models
Entity that contain data, repository interfaces,bussiness logic(use cases)

Data Layer-> it contains data
Database,api interface,Repository implementation

dto -> data transfer object ye object hota hai jo api return krta hai


repository package do jgh es liye hai ki
domain layer me bs define hoga
data layer me repository implementtion hoga
ye testcases k liye bht helpful hota hai



Use case -> should only have one public function
humne invoke function ko override kiya hai taki  use cases ko as a function use kr ske




